00035 void TBTrackMokkaCheck::initHists() {
00036 
00037   std::string sxy[2]={"X","Y"};
00038   std::string sly[4]={"Layer0","Layer1","Layer2","Layer3"};
00039   
00040   hNCol=new TH1F("NCol","Number of hit collections",9,0.0,9.0);
00041   hNEnt=new TH1F("NEnt","Number of events with hit object 4*XY+Layer",8,0.0,8.0);
00042 
00043   for(unsigned xy(0);xy<2;xy++) {
00044     for(unsigned layer(0);layer<4;layer++) {
00045       hNumb[xy][layer]=new TH1F((sxy[xy]+sly[layer]+"Numb").c_str(),
00046                                 (sxy[xy]+" "+sly[layer]+": Number of hits").c_str(),
00047                                 100,0.0,100.0);
00048       hCell[xy][layer]=new TH1F((sxy[xy]+sly[layer]+"Cell").c_str(),
00049                                 (sxy[xy]+" "+sly[layer]+": Hit distribution").c_str(),
00050                                 8,0.0,8.0);
00051       hPosn[xy][layer]=new TH1F((sxy[xy]+sly[layer]+"Posn").c_str(),
00052                                 (sxy[xy]+" "+sly[layer]+": Hit position (mm)").c_str(),
00053                                 100,-50.0,50.0);
00054       hPosz[xy][layer]=new TH1F((sxy[xy]+sly[layer]+"Posz").c_str(),
00055                                 (sxy[xy]+" "+sly[layer]+": Hit z position (mm)").c_str(),
00056                                 1000,-10000.0,0.0);
00057       hEner[xy][layer]=new TH1F((sxy[xy]+sly[layer]+"Ener").c_str(),
00058                                 (sxy[xy]+" "+sly[layer]+": Hit energy (MeV)").c_str(),
00059                                 100,0.0,0.0005);
00060       hTime[xy][layer]=new TH1F((sxy[xy]+sly[layer]+"Time").c_str(),
00061                                 (sxy[xy]+" "+sly[layer]+": Hit time (ns)").c_str(),
00062                                 1500,0.0,150.0/10000.0);
00063       hTana[xy][layer]=new TH1F((sxy[xy]+sly[layer]+"Tana").c_str(),
00064                                 (sxy[xy]+" "+sly[layer]+": Hit tan(angle)").c_str(),
00065                                 100,-0.01,0.01);
00066     }
00067   }
00068 }

00079 void TBTrackMokkaCheck::ProcessEvent( LCEvent * evt ) {
00080 
00081   //the following access the names of the collection.
00082   // having the name, we can access the collection itself by calling 
00083   // LCCollection *mycol = evt->getCollection(*name);
00084 
00085   typedef const std::vector<std::string> StringVec;
00086   StringVec* strVec = evt->getCollectionNames();
00087   for( StringVec::const_iterator name = strVec->begin(); name != strVec->end(); name++) {
00088       
00089     std::string sss = name->c_str();
00090     LCCollection* col = evt->getCollection(*name);
00091     int nHits =  col->getNumberOfElements();
00092     
00093     if (printLevel(3)) std::cout << "EXISTING COLLECTION, of the class : "
00094                                  << col->getTypeName().c_str()
00095                                  << " and named : " << sss << " with "
00096                                  << nHits << " elements." << std::endl;
00097   }
00098   
00099 
00100 
00101 
00102   const LCCollection *c(0);
00103 
00104   if((c=getCollection(evt,"MCParticle",LCIO::MCPARTICLE))!=0) {
00105     if(c->getNumberOfElements()<1) {
00106       if(printLevel(-2)) std::cout << "Number of MCParticles = "
00107                                    << c->getNumberOfElements() << std::endl;
00108     } else {
00109       if(printLevel(2)) std::cout << "Number of MCParticles = "
00110                                 << c->getNumberOfElements() << std::endl;
00111       for(int i(0);i<c->getNumberOfElements();i++) {
00112         if(printLevel(3)) std::cout << "MCParticles " << i << std::endl;
00113       }
00114     }
00115   }
00116   
00117 
00118 
00119     unsigned nCol(0);
00120     LCCollection *col;                          
00121   for(int l(0);l<4;l++) {
00122     col=0;
00123     try{
00124       if(l==0) col = evt->getCollection("TBdch02_dchSD2"); //DC1 and DC2 are swapped
00125       if(l==1) col = evt->getCollection("TBdch02_dchSD1"); //DC1 and DC2 are swapped
00126       if(l==2) col = evt->getCollection("TBdch02_dchSD3");
00127       if(l==3) col = evt->getCollection("TBdch02_dchSD4");
00128       
00129     } catch ( DataNotAvailableException &e) {
00130       
00131       try{
00132         if(l==0) col = evt->getCollection("TBdch04_dchSD3");
00133         if(l==1) col = evt->getCollection("TBdch04_dchSD2");
00134         if(l==2) col = evt->getCollection("TBdch04_dchSD1");
00135         
00136       } catch ( DataNotAvailableException &e) {
00137         std::cout << "Problem in TDC Collection, incorrect name?" << std::endl;
00138       }
00139     }
00140     
00141     double energy(0.0);
00142     double xe(0.0),ye(0.0);
00143     
00144     if(col!=0) {
00145       assert(col->getTypeName()==LCIO::SIMTRACKERHIT);
00146       
00147       nCol++;
00148       hNEnt->Fill(2*l);
00149 
00150       //    std::cout << "Number of elements = "
00151       //      << col->getNumberOfElements() << std::endl;
00152       
00153       for(int i(0);i<col->getNumberOfElements();i++) {
00154         const SimTrackerHit *p(dynamic_cast<const SimTrackerHit*>(col->getElementAt(i)));
00155         assert(p!=0);
00156         //assert(p->getCellID()==l);
00157 
00158         hCell[0][l]->Fill(p->getCellID());
00159         hPosn[0][l]->Fill(p->getPosition()[0]);
00160         hPosz[0][l]->Fill(p->getPosition()[2]);
00161         hEner[0][l]->Fill(p->getdEdx()*p->getPathLength());
00162         //hTime[0][l]->Fill(10000.0*p->getTime());
00163         hTime[0][l]->Fill(p->getTime());
00164         if(p->getMomentum()[2]!=0.0)
00165           hTana[0][l]->Fill(p->getMomentum()[0]/p->getMomentum()[2]);
00166 
00167         /*
00168         std::cout << l << ", "
00169                   << p->getCellID() << ", "
00170                   << p->getPosition()[0] << ", "
00171                   << p->getPosition()[1] << ", "
00172                   << p->getPosition()[2] << ", "
00173                   << p->getdEdx() << ", "
00174                   << p->getTime() << ", "
00175                   << p->getMomentum()[0] << ", "
00176                   << p->getMomentum()[1] << ", "
00177                   << p->getMomentum()[2] << ", "
00178                   << p->getPathLength() << std::endl;
00179         */
00180         //double speed((35000.0+p->getPosition()[2])/(10000.0*p->getTime()));
00181         //std::cout << "speed, E = " << speed << std::endl;
00182 
00183         energy+=p->getdEdx()*p->getPathLength();
00184         xe+=p->getdEdx()*p->getPathLength()*p->getPosition()[0];
00185         ye+=p->getdEdx()*p->getPathLength()*p->getPosition()[1];
00186       }
00187       //std::cout << "Energy " << energy << ", average x " 
00188       //        << xe/energy << ", y " << ye/energy << std::endl;
00189     }
00190   }
00191 
00192   hNCol->Fill(nCol);
00193 }
